can be reflected in reality.

62
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:35,550
Dad, why are you video calling me again?

63
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:36,610
What's the matter?

64
00:04:36,970 --> 00:04:38,830
[When I went for a jog yesterday,]

65
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:40,670
[I saw a house.]

66
