[It's quite affordable.]

71
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:55,050
[It's the price of a two-bedroom
in Xiamen.]

72
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:56,620
[I think it's nice.]

73
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:59,450
