88
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:53,430
it's making me even more sad.

89
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,400
[A lot of words have been said]

90
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:59,900
[about relationships.]

91
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:04,370
[But none is better than
when you figure it out yourself.]

92
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,660
But, you know,

93
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:12,020
you need time to figure it out.

94
00:06:12,730 --> 00:06:15,380
You need time and space.

95
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:27,210
Actually, these two days
I've been thinking

96
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,950
whether I should go over for a bit.

97
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:36,650
Duan Ran found a new job recently.

98
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:39,300
He just got himself together

99
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,980
and is starting over.

100
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,590
In a new environment,

101
00:06:42,590 --> 00:06:43,900
he needs to deal with lots of new stuff.

102
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:46,100
There are many things he has to adapt to.

103
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:49,180
I don't want to tell him now.

104
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,550
He will have a hard time
facing me and Aunt Zhou.

105
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:56,110
[That's right.]

106
00:06:57,490 --> 00:06:59,950
[I'll pay the deposit
for that house later.]

107
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,640
Wait. So fast?

108
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:06,860
[I still have a lot of things
that I haven't dealt with.]

109
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:08,690
After I settle my stuff here

110
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:09,780
and get my visa,

111
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:10,870
I'll inform you, alright?

112
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:14,830
[Alright. Tell me when you're ready.]

113
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,580
[I'll be waiting for you.]

114
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:11,110
Whose boyfriend is this?
Such a handsome man.

115
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,900
You finally showed up.

116
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,680
You didn't answer my calls

117
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:20,450
and my messages.

118
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:23,060
Were you expecting me to call the cops?

119
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,670
I was busy.

120
00:08:26,290 --> 00:08:28,820
I'm busy launching
the second season of Vine.

121
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:29,880
It's your fault.

122
00:08:29,970 --> 00:08:32,120
You told Ouyang to leave
the independent brand to me.

123
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,250
Now I'm drowning.

124
00:08:35,289 --> 00:08:36,970
The first day Vine was launched,

125
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:39,299
Ding Ding snatched it from you, didn't he?

126
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,289
How did you know that?

127
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:44,270
Why not?

128
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:45,940
I'll take you around.

129
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:50,700
Where to?

130
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:53,060
Buy you a gift in the mall.

131
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,500
I saw a nice ring.

132
00:08:54,580 --> 00:08:55,640
I'll buy it for you.

133
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,150
Duan Ran,

134
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:00,850
you just found a job

135
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:03,400
and you're buying me
such an expensive gift?

136
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:06,460
How hard can earning money be to me?

137
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,450
Forget it. I don't want it yet.

138
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:13,140
What's wrong?

139
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:16,740
Nothing. It's just that
I haven't been feeling myself recently.

140
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:18,150
Too many things happened at work.

141
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:21,550
When I feel better,
I'll take my time and choose one, alright?

142
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:24,940
That's an excuse.

143
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:28,710
Fine. Then what do you want to do?

144
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,790
I'm hungry, are you?

145
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,240
You brought food?

146
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:36,460
Fish balls!

147
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:39,000
Who told you my favourite is fish balls?

148
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,500
Then what's your favourite?

149
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:41,650
Egg tarts.

150
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:43,180
Let's share a box.

151
00:09:58,460 --> 00:10:00,130
We only kept talking about me.

152
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:01,640
How about you? You got a new job.

153
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,100
Have you gotten used to it?

154
00:10:04,290 --> 00:10:07,290
Every day has been productive.
I've many things to do.

155
00:10:07,300 --> 00:10:09,820
I get to see many types
of people in the mall.

156
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,910
It's quite nice.

157
00:10:13,070 --> 00:10:15,420
Everyday, I watch so many people

158
00:10:15,590 --> 00:10:17,030
going back and forth.

159
00:10:17,230 --> 00:10:18,730
They have different emotions,

160
00:10:18,730 --> 00:10:19,980
different conditions

161
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:21,420
and different expressions.

162
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,350
As I listen to them
telling different stories,

163
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:25,350
I can also experience many stories.

164
00:10:29,130 --> 00:10:31,540
I thought you're working in QE
as a floor manager

165
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:34,200
so that you get to experience life
in the future.

166
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:36,830
I am experiencing life.

167
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:38,850
If I tell you

168
00:10:38,970 --> 00:10:40,050
that you're making excuses,

169
00:10:40,050 --> 00:10:41,170
will you admit it?

170
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,560
You're running away from it.

171
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,830
Back in Rui,

172
00:10:50,410 --> 00:10:52,700
we worked so hard
and put all our efforts in.

173
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:54,280
But no matter how hard we worked,

174
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:57,480
Shen Ding Ding took everything from us
with just one word.

175
00:10:58,210 --> 00:11:00,410
But what if you were there?
What if you had stayed?

176
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:01,410
If you had stayed,

177
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,360
things could've been different.

178
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:06,350
At least I'd feel happy
seeing you everyday.

179
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:08,110
You give me energy.

180
00:11:12,290 --> 00:11:13,410
Xi Xi.

181
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:16,620
Please understand my feelings.

182
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,210
What happened to Rui

183
00:11:19,310 --> 00:11:21,950
had opened my eyes to the world.

184
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:25,980
Give me some time to find my way,
will you?

185
00:11:35,810 --> 00:11:37,890
Should I go abroad for a while?

186
00:11:39,690 --> 00:11:41,010
My dad told me

187
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:44,030
he wants me to spend some time with him.

188
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,470
Should we

189
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,700
take a break?

190
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:17,470
It's because of me.

191
00:12:21,660 --> 00:12:23,230
When I was down,

192
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:25,740
what did you do?

193
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:29,080
You'd stay by my side every single day.

194
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:33,260
You talked to me and reasoned with me.

195
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:34,790
You brought me hope

196
00:12:35,170 --> 00:12:36,700
and let me see the sunlight.

197
00:12:37,830 --> 00:12:39,950
But now you're feeling down.

198
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:42,710
Why can't I do the same for you?

199
00:12:43,190 --> 00:12:45,480
I can't calm you down

200
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:49,100
or make you feel better.

201
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,590
Besides, I affect you with my negativity.

202
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,960
I'd ignore your calls,

203
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:57,170
or like what I did earlier,

204
00:12:57,170 --> 00:12:58,970
I'd mention these things again.

205
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:02,620
Xi Xi.

206
00:13:06,470 --> 00:13:08,000
I know what you're feeling.

207
00:13:08,330 --> 00:13:09,840
I also know

208
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:12,830
that everyone
has different attitudes and expressions

209
00:13:12,830 --> 00:13:14,590
while facing the same things. I get it.

210
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:16,790
I know you're doing this for my own good.

211
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:29,490
I think I failed terribly
as your girlfriend.

212
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:39,660
Up until today, I've failed terribly.

213
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:07,700
Go ahead.

214
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:10,500
Uncle Qian has been staying abroad
for so many years.

215
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,830
He wants you to go there.

216
00:14:12,470 --> 00:14:13,590
I get it.

217
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:14,950
I totally get it.

218
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:16,940
You should go.

219
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:22,410
But don't you mention breaking up.

220
00:14:23,590 --> 00:14:25,250
Don't you ever say that again.

221
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:27,990
Duan Ran.

222
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:30,310
Let's go home for dinner next week.

223
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:32,180
I'll ask my mum to cook something nice.

224
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:34,510
We'll hold a farewell party for you, okay?

225
00:14:37,830 --> 00:14:38,880
Be good.

226
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,290
If you're ready,

227
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,980
put up a sign.

228
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:15,980
Okay, let's start.

229
00:15:22,910 --> 00:15:25,840
It's been a while
since I last stood on this platform.

230
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,060
After our account was suspended,

231
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:30,410
I kind of missed this place.

232
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:35,460
Look.

233
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:39,120
My mental support during live stream

234
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:40,390
is all in here.

235
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,290
I used to put a high stool here.

236
00:15:43,470 --> 00:15:44,490
I'd squat on it.

237
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:46,870
At times, I'd stand up, squat or sit down,

238
00:15:46,900 --> 00:15:48,270
-I'd instruct them from here.
-Really?

239
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:49,150
Yes.

240
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:52,950
But I don't need it today,

241
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:56,750
because my mental support
is standing right next to me today.

242
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:00,540
You just hired a new batch
of broadcasters.

243
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:02,360
It's just the first step
of your moon landing plan.

244
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:04,410
After that, you have to train them,

245
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:06,080
build them an image,

246
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:07,580
build up their fans circle,

247
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:09,650
and look for a suitable direction

248
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:11,060
and brands for them.

249
00:16:11,910 --> 00:16:12,790
Look.

250
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:15,400
I've achieved
the first step of moon landing.

251
00:16:15,530 --> 00:16:18,460
Aren't I getting closer
to conquering the universe?

252
00:16:21,830 --> 00:16:22,710
Jia Yun,

253
00:16:23,090 --> 00:16:24,910
are you free this weekend?

254
00:16:25,410 --> 00:16:27,670
I have a classmate reunion this weekend.

255
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:39,150
In fact, I can skip it.

256
00:16:42,100 --> 00:16:43,460
Can you?

257
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,300
I guess so.

258
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:50,010
When I was talking to Mr Wu back then,

259
00:16:50,090 --> 00:16:51,590
I have so many mixed feelings.

260
00:16:51,590 --> 00:16:53,490
We talked about the supply chain.

261
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:55,470
I think,

262
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:57,060
I should invite our Miss Zhang here

263
00:16:57,060 --> 00:16:58,790
to the clothing market with me,

264
00:16:58,970 --> 00:17:01,220
so that you can advise me
on the supply chain.

265
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:02,870
I can't decide by myself.

266
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:05,569
Then I guess

267
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:07,630
I have to learn from Mr Chen as well.

268
00:17:13,990 --> 00:17:14,900
Uncle Duan,

269
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:15,900
Aunt Zhou.

270
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:18,060
After I leave,

271
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:19,460
I guess I won't be seeing you

272
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:20,829
for quite some time.

273
00:17:21,650 --> 00:17:23,990
Here.
I brought this protein powder for you.

274
00:17:23,990 --> 00:17:25,420
Keep this at home

275
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:27,829
and make a cup for yourself every morning.

276
00:17:29,670 --> 00:17:31,380
Xi Xi is such a good girl.

