00:31:01,930 --> 00:31:03,260
I'll call you whenever I miss you.

559
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:04,140
Good.

560
00:31:06,570 --> 00:31:07,520
Xi Xi.

561
00:31:08,570 --> 00:31:10,260
I will do a check-up soon.

562
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:13,220
If everything goes well with the check-up,

563
00:31:13,370 --> 00:31:14,580
Aunt Zhou and I

564
00:31:14,730 --> 00:31:16,240
will visit you and your dad.

565
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,320
That's great.

566
00:31:17,410 --> 00:31:18,620
You should go there soon.

567
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:20,540
My dad will be thrilled.

568
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:24,220
Alright, you don't have to see me off.

569
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:27,610
Come, give me a hug.

570
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:32,120
I'm off.

571
00:32:28,090 --> 00:32:29,700
After leaving,

572
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:32,420
you have to take care of yourself.

573
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:35,680
If something happens, don't worry.

574
00:32:35,910 --> 00:32:36,970
Your brother's here.

575
00:32:36,970 --> 00:32:38,570
Call me if there's anything.

576
00:32:43,950 --> 00:32:46,440
Did you hear me? Did you hear me?

577
00:32:48,610 --> 00:32:50,780
Be gentle, I heard you.

578
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:58,570
A brother should do his duty.

579
00:32:59,650 --> 00:33:02,450
Stay here with Uncle Duan and Aunt Zhou.

580
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,810
Take good care of them.

581
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:10,850
Don't worry about me.

582
00:33:11,530 --> 00:33:14,020
Just take good care of yourself.

583
00:33:16,380 --> 00:33:18,110
I will take good care of myself.

584
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:24,240
Alright, I have to leave.

585
00:33:24,370 --> 00:33:26,090
Okay. Go ahead, go.

586
00:33:35,390 --> 00:33:36,270
See you.

587
00:34:16,909 --> 00:34:22,460
[Bank card]

588
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:35,840
Have you received the admission letter?

589
00:34:39,699 --> 00:34:41,060
I will leave tomorrow.

590
00:34:42,530 --> 00:34:44,330
You seemed to be concerned

591
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,750
about Cloud Live and me.

592
00:34:45,870 --> 00:34:47,000
I thought

593
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,889
you would stay here and manage it with me.

594
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:51,830
Chen Lang,

595
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:56,270
I came to see you today

596
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:58,110
to bid you farewell.

597
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,200
You'll be on your own from now on.

598
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,160
In fact,

599
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:08,110
we are not meant to be together.

600
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:13,590
I know.

601
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:17,720
I really don't want
to burden you any more.

602
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,870
Just like what you said,

603
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:21,220
we are young people

604
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,760
who came from a small town.

605
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:24,550
Life has given us

606
00:35:24,640 --> 00:35:26,750
way too many burdens.

607
00:35:27,830 --> 00:35:30,240
I can no longer be a burden in your life.

608
00:35:31,720 --> 00:35:34,030
For example, the incident
with our own brand.

609
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,180
If it weren't for me,

610
00:35:35,270 --> 00:35:38,270
you wouldn't have been so easily used
by Ding Ding.

611
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,400
You're still upset about this, aren't you?

612
00:35:45,350 --> 00:35:46,320
You know,

613
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:48,660
if you keep pursuing

614
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:50,550
things that don't belong to you,

615
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:52,510
hankering over tons of things,

616
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:55,000
you will be trapped by these things

617
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,110
and never find happiness.

618
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,310
Jia Yun,

619
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:09,690
we were talking about The Little Prince
in the car earlier.

620
00:36:09,690 --> 00:36:10,750
Do you remember?

621
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:15,310
Although I'm not a prince,

622
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:19,480
I really consider you my rose.

623
00:36:20,990 --> 00:36:24,380
I will stay by you my whole life.

624
00:36:27,490 --> 00:36:29,510
By all means, just go to England.

625
00:36:33,290 --> 00:36:34,570
No matter how long,

626
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,520
I'll wait for you.

627
00:36:45,650 --> 00:36:48,160
Look, the sunset is beautiful.

628
00:36:54,870 --> 00:36:56,810
But, no matter
how beautiful the sunset it,

629
00:36:56,810 --> 00:36:58,500
it's just an ordinary event.

630
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:02,040
It's an ordinary event
which you can never change.

631
00:37:07,070 --> 00:37:09,400
We have to learn to give up.

632
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:13,350
Otherwise, how can we find happiness?

633
00:37:21,610 --> 00:37:22,560
Jia Yun.

634
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:27,680
Do you know why I like sunsets so much?

635
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:33,350
It's just like my feelings for you.

636
00:37:35,410 --> 00:37:38,620
I know it will sink little by little,

637
00:37:40,310 --> 00:37:43,440
but it will rise as usual the next day.

638
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,790
That's how much I like you.

639
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:52,280
There's no way I can change it.

640
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:19,740
What's the matter? Why did you ask me

641
00:38:19,830 --> 00:38:21,510
to such a romantic place?

642
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:26,680
I want to enjoy the sea breeze
and relax a little.

643
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:29,960
Did something happen?

644
00:38:32,350 --> 00:38:33,960
Xi Xi rejected me again.

645
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:36,440
This time, she completely rejected me.

646
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:37,830
There are certain things

647
00:38:37,830 --> 00:38:39,160
which you have to let go

648
00:38:39,270 --> 00:38:40,640
when you have to.

649
00:38:41,830 --> 00:38:43,660
I think, letting go

650
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:45,550
means you stop competing with it

651
00:38:45,680 --> 00:38:47,740
and also stop being hard on yourself.

652
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:53,020
Sometimes, just giving
is already enough.

653
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,720
But this kind of devotion

654
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:58,150
is also a kind of tribute to your love.

655
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:01,230
If she rejects you or turns you down,

656
00:39:01,230 --> 00:39:02,590
that's normal.

657
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,860
It's not her fault.

658
00:39:06,350 --> 00:39:07,720
But I think,

659
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:10,220
what if fate comes

660
00:39:10,310 --> 00:39:12,430
and I find someone whom I love even more?

661
00:39:12,430 --> 00:39:14,830
Besides, you're so young, right?

662
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:17,100
Tens of thousands of girls like you.

663
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:18,480
What are you afraid of?

664
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,510
Who knows,
you might even meet the right girl

665
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:22,440
when you're on your way back later.

666
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,200
That is why I said,

667
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:27,300
when it's time to move on,
then you should.

668
00:39:28,180 --> 00:39:30,840
Ouyang, you're really carefree.

669
00:39:33,750 --> 00:39:35,750
Actually, I was thinking about something.

670
00:39:35,750 --> 00:39:37,550
It's actually quite easy

671
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:40,000
to figure them out.

672
00:39:40,830 --> 00:39:43,750
Never underestimate
the power of companionship.

673
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:46,440
They grew up together
and lived together since young.

674
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:49,040
Now they're working together
and starting a business together.

675
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,060
Rain or shine,

676
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:52,160
they went through so many things together.

677
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:54,680
To be honest,

678
00:39:54,830 --> 00:39:57,560
I think it's hard for others
to stand in their way.

679
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:02,150
Then,

680
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:04,440
if they can do it, why can't we?

681
00:40:05,780 --> 00:40:06,870
Do what?

682
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:08,600
Start a business!

683
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:11,830
How can you jump from this topic to that?

684
00:40:11,830 --> 00:40:13,110
Starting a business?

685
00:40:19,200 --> 00:40:20,150
You have no idea.

686
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:23,160
After you left,
the whole team has lost its unity.

687
00:40:23,350 --> 00:40:25,550
When you were there,
I didn't have to worry about a thing.

688
00:40:25,550 --> 00:40:26,510
But now,

689
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,040
I even have to teach them.

690
00:40:28,860 --> 00:40:31,060
So, seriously, the best thing for me

691
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,800
is to work together with you.

692
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:34,480
But Yang Yang, I mean it.

693
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,590
There can only be one decision maker
in a company.

694
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:40,110
If I go back, won't things be the same?

695
00:40:40,780 --> 00:40:42,920
Ouyang, listen to me.

696
00:40:43,950 --> 00:40:45,710
I listened to my mum

697
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:46,960
because I wanted to be a good son.

698
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:48,240
You know it too.

699
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:52,440
So, if you really do come back,

700
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,880
I will talk to my mum.

701
00:41:17,250 --> 00:41:18,390
So,

702
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,760
you don't plan to tell Duan Ran
about Aunt Zhou?

703
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,470
You're afraid that he'll be guilty

704
00:41:24,790 --> 00:41:27,640
and your relationship
won't be so simple any more.

705
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:33,790
Only Jia Yun knows me best.

706
00:41:35,550 --> 00:41:37,830
Seriously, when I heard

707
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:41,400
that Aunt Zhou indirectly
caused my mother's car accident,

708
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:44,550
I felt like the sky was falling.

709
00:41:45,640 --> 00:41:47,470
I can't imagine what Duan Ran would think

710
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,350
if he finds out.

711
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:50,030
It concerns the two of you.

712
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:53,280
It might be better
if both of you solve it together.

713
00:41:53,910 --> 00:41:55,240
Look. What you just said

714
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:58,190
was the assumption you made
about Duan Ran.

715
00:41:58,750 --> 00:42:00,110
In fact, you don't really know

716
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:01,790
what he will do.

717
00:42:03,690 --> 00:42:04,960
I dare not ask him.

718
00:42:05,900 --> 00:42:07,530
I'm not confident as well.

719
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,710
I love Duan Ran.

720
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:16,440
He is like my other life.

721
00:42:17,140 --> 00:42:19,870
But I really can't face
Aunt Zhou's predicament.

722
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:21,350
I don't know what to do.

723
00:42:22,510 --> 00:42:24,570
So you chose to run away from it.

724
00:42:26,340 --> 00:42:27,480
No.

725
00:42:28,230 --> 00:42:30,150
Now, I chose

726
00:42:30,380 --> 00:42:32,410
to let time tell me the answer.

727
00:42:36,750 --> 00:42:38,660
Such a passive attitude

728
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:41,880
is not that Qian Xi Xi
whom I'm familiar with.

729
00:42:44,160 --> 00:42:47,100
I can be impulsive and direct,

730
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:49,250
but I can't hurt other people.

731
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:51,880
If I stay,

732
00:42:52,470 --> 00:42:55,550
Aunt Zhou will definitely be very sad.

733
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:58,010
Uncle Duan will be in a dilemma.

734
00:42:59,120 --> 00:43:00,700
And if Duan Ran finds out,

735
00:43:00,830 --> 00:43:01,880
I really have no idea

736
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:03,590
what choice he will make.

737
00:43:05,710 --> 00:43:07,400
Anyway, I made my choice.

738
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:10,060
What about you?

739
00:43:10,790 --> 00:43:12,920
I've also talked things over with him.

740
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:14,700
Anyway, this is life.

741
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:17,720
There are ups and downs,
meetings and farewells.

742
00:43:17,720 --> 00:43:18,920
Just go with the flow.

743
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:20,270
As for you,

744
00:43:20,360 --> 00:43:21,690
I'll just stay with you.

745
00:43:22,730 --> 00:43:23,660
What's wrong?

746
00:43:23,740 --> 00:43:24,830
Xi Xi.

747
00:43:26,150 --> 00:43:28,200
You are my best friend.

748
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:30,180
I mean it. I think

749
00:43:30,270 --> 00:43:32,540
you're always so straightforward,

750
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:35,230
brave and direct.

751
00:43:35,700 --> 00:43:37,550
You made a passive person like me

752
00:43:38,010 --> 00:43:39,570
improve a lot.
